'''氣旋若亞敬'''（{{lang-en|Cyclone Joachim}} ），是一股在2011年12月中旬造成西歐地區重大破壞的溫帶氣旋，其在法國[[多姆山省|多姆山省]]測得高達{{convert|212|km/h|m/s mph}}的最大[[陣風|陣風]]<ref name="212 kmh winds">{{cite news|title=La tempête Joachim des 15 et 16 décembre 2011|url=http://france.meteofrance.com/france/actu/actu?document_id=26158&portlet_id=78817|accessdate=2011-12-28|newspaper=Meteo France|date=2011-12-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Severe Storm Joachim Unleashes Hurricane Force Winds|url=http://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news/new-storm-set-to-lash-france/59039|publisher=accuweather.com|accessdate=2012-02-13|archive-date=2012-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120117205101/http://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news/new-storm-set-to-lash-france/59039|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。若亞敬在其發展過程中，被觀測到其受[[高空槽|短波槽]]的影響而產生[[爆發性旋生|爆發性旋生]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Karremann|first1=Melanie K.|last2=Liberato|first2=Margarida L. R.|last3=Ordóñez|first3=Paulina|last4=Pinto|first4=Joaquim G.|title=Characterization of synoptic conditions and cyclones associated with top ranking potential wind loss events over Iberia|journal=Atmospheric Science Letters|date=2016年6月|volume=17|issue=6|pages=354–361|doi=10.1002/asl.665|url=https://publikationen.bibliothek.kit.edu/1000055458/3854408|access-date=2020-08-13|archive-date=2018-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719160825/https://publikationen.bibliothek.kit.edu/1000055458/3854408|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
==影響==
受到若亞敬的影響，TK布萊梅號貨輪在法國[[布列塔尼大區|布列塔尼大區]]西北側海岸擱淺後，貨輪在19名船員被直升機救援後爆炸<ref>{{cite news|title=Coverage on francetv.fr|url=http://www.francetv.fr/info/le-passage-de-la-tempete-joachim-en-images_39993.html|newspaper=francetv}}</ref>。在若亞敬影響期間，法國總共超過40萬戶家庭停電<ref name=francepower>{{cite news|title=STORM CAUSES BLACKOUT IN NORTH-WEST OF FRANCE|url=http://www.agi.it/english-version/world/elenco-notizie/201112161526-cro-ren1057-storm_causes_blackout_in_north_west_of_france|accessdate=27 December 2011|newspaper=AGI|date=2011-12-16|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130218113117/http://www.agi.it/english-version/world/elenco-notizie/201112161526-cro-ren1057-storm_causes_blackout_in_north_west_of_france|archive-date=2013-02-18}}</ref> ，且影響陸上及空中交通狀況<ref>{{cite web|title=Power cuts, oil spills and cancelled trains as Storm Joachim lashes France|url=http://www.english.rfi.fr/environment/20111216-power-cuts-oil-spills-and-cancelled-trains-storm-joachim-lashes-france|publisher=rfi.fr|accessdate=2012-02-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304121721/http://www.english.rfi.fr/environment/20111216-power-cuts-oil-spills-and-cancelled-trains-storm-joachim-lashes-france|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。瑞士在此次事件中，有民眾回報有屋頂及樹木遭氣旋吹倒，政府亦禁止船隻在風暴期間於湖上航行<ref>{{cite web|title=Storm Joachim arrives in Switzerland|url=http://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/swiss_news/Storm_Joachim_arrives_in_Switzerland.html?cid=31776866|publisher=swissinfo.ch|accessdate=2012-02-13}}</ref> 。根據Perils AG公司的評估，認為[[財產保險|財產保險]]公司可能在此次風暴受到3億[[歐元|歐元]]的損失<ref>{{cite web|title=Storm Joachim May Cost Insurers 300 Million Euros, Perils Says|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-26/storm-joachim-may-cost-insurers-300-million-euros-perils-says.html|publisher=Bloomberg|accessdate=2012-02-13|archive-date=2012-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225110021/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-26/storm-joachim-may-cost-insurers-300-million-euros-perils-says.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

